	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just found this message board and noticed that the gameboy section was a ghost town. I have also posted on the nintendoage forums and they said that the fanbase is very small due to the gba. I am worried that if i start developing my own game that it will go downhill due to little or no support. Any assistance in this matter would be greatly appreciated.
