	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What do you mean downhill or little support exactly? In the past the Gameboy had quite a bit of resources available for programming homebrew. There is no reason there would be less of that now. If you want to make a Gameboy game, do it. While there isn't a ton of activity in this forum it certainly isn't ignored. If you have questions someone will try their best to answer or point you in the direction of the answers.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
